Dialogue: 100,0:00:03.48,0:00:05.66,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}啊! 这样根本不会有进展\N{\rENG}Guh! This isn't getting us anywhere. 
Dialogue: 100,0:00:05.66,0:00:07.36,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}怎么了 "煎饺"?\N{\rENG}What's the matter, perogie? 
Dialogue: 100,0:00:07.36,0:00:07.96,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你累了?\N{\rENG}You tired? 
Dialogue: 100,0:00:07.96,0:00:10.46,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我不要疲惫 我只要结果\N{\rENG}I don't get tired. I get results. 
Dialogue: 100,0:00:13.72,0:00:17.47,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}"拉我起来"的标志是晃一下还是晃两下?\N{\rENG}Was the sign for "pull me up"one wiggle or two? 
Dialogue: 100,0:00:17.47,0:00:19.31,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}紫晶 保持注意力\N{\rENG}Amethyst, stay focused. 
Dialogue: 100,0:00:20.01,0:00:22.17,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}就我们所知 青金石和碧玉的融合体\N{\rENG}For all we know, Lapis and Jasper's fusion
Dialogue: 100,0:00:22.18,0:00:23.98,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}可能就在眼前\N{\rENG}could be right under our noses. 
Dialogue: 100,0:00:25.51,0:00:28.08,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}这就是我们要穿救生衣的原因\N{\rENG}This is why we wear life jackets. 
Dialogue: 100,0:00:28.08,0:00:30.52,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你-你还好吗?\N{\rENG}Are--are you all right? 
Dialogue: 100,0:00:30.52,0:00:32.58,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}什么也没有\N{\rENG}Nothing. 
Dialogue: 100,0:00:34.66,0:00:35.85,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}哦 感觉\N{\rENG}Oh, it feels like
Dialogue: 100,0:00:35.86,0:00:38.09,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我们已经搜索了好几"光年"了\N{\rENG}we've been searching for light years. 
Dialogue: 100,0:00:38.09,0:00:40.09,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}呃 "光年"测的是光\N{\rENG}Uh, light years measures light. 
Dialogue: 100,0:00:40.09,0:00:41.93,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}不是年\N{\rENG} Not years. 
Dialogue: 100,0:00:43.13,0:00:46.78,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我受够这些..."救生尿布"了\N{\rENG}And I'm sick of these...Life diapers. 
Dialogue: 100,0:00:46.88,0:00:49.30,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}安全不是玩笑 珍珠\N{\rENG}Safety is no punch line, Pearl. 
Dialogue: 100,0:00:49.32,0:00:51.16,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}安全就是我们的任务\N{\rENG}Safety is our job. 
Dialogue: 100,0:00:51.18,0:00:52.84,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我们必须找到青金石和碧玉\N{\rENG}We must find Jasper and Lapis. 
Dialogue: 100,0:00:52.84,0:00:53.97,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}只要还存在\N{\rENG}As it stands, 
Dialogue: 100,0:00:53.97,0:00:55.94,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}她们的融合体就是定时炸弹\N{\rENG}their fusion is a ticking time bomb. 
Dialogue: 100,0:00:56.16,0:00:58.56,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}青金石不会出事吧?\N{\rENG}Is Lapis gonna be okay? 
Dialogue: 100,0:00:58.62,0:01:00.44,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}她使用能力将她们的融合体\N{\rENG}She had control when she used her power
Dialogue: 100,0:01:00.46,0:01:02.05,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}拖入海中时 她是清醒的\N{\rENG}to drag their fusion into the ocean, 
Dialogue: 100,0:01:02.34,0:01:04.85,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}但是 像她们那样由猜忌和愤怒\N{\rENG}but a fusion like theirs is unstable, 
Dialogue: 100,0:01:04.85,0:01:06.92,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}束缚在一起融合体是不稳定的\N{\rENG}bound together by anger and mistrust. 
Dialogue: 100,0:01:07.06,0:01:08.36,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}一旦约束被打破\N{\rENG}If that bond snaps, 
Dialogue: 100,0:01:08.36,0:01:11.89,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}她们的愤怒会彻底释放 摧毁一切\N{\rENG}their anger will take over and destroy. 
Dialogue: 100,0:01:12.86,0:01:14.23,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}不要担心 青金石\N{\rENG}Don't worry, Lapis. 
Dialogue: 100,0:01:14.23,0:01:16.46,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我们不会让你和鱼群入睡的\N{\rENG}We won't let you sleep with the fishes. 
Dialogue: 600,0:01:14.23,0:01:16.46,Hint,,0,0,0,,短语"sleep with the fishes"出自著名黑手党电影"教父"
Dialogue: 100,0:01:17.47,0:01:20.00,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我们得继续搜索\N{\rENG}We're gonna have to keep looking. 
Dialogue: 100,0:01:20.00,0:01:22.67,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}但首先 我们要把史蒂文带回家\N{\rENG}But first, let's bring Steven home. 
Dialogue: 100,0:01:22.67,0:01:24.30,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}呃? 蛤?\N{\rENG}Huh? What? Wha? 
Dialogue: 100,0:01:24.31,0:01:26.81,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}不. 我-我-我没事\N{\rENG}No. I'm--I'm--I'm fine. 
Dialogue: 100,0:01:26.81,0:01:28.34,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}一起-一起钓鱼吧\N{\rENG}Let's--let's go fishing. 
Dialogue: 100,0:01:28.34,0:01:31.54,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}第一个抓到东西的获胜\N{\rENG}First one to catch something wins. 
Dialogue: 100,0:01:31.55,0:01:32.62,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我赢了\N{\rENG}I win. 
Dialogue: 600,0:01:31.55,0:01:32.62,Hint,,0,0,0,,此处Steven的姿势致敬"最终幻想"系列中的仙人掌
Dialogue: 100,0:01:33.34,0:01:35.25,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我们本应在外面搜索\N{\rENG}We should be out there searching, 
Dialogue: 100,0:01:35.25,0:01:37.98,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}而不是在这里发呆\N{\rENG}not in here not searching. 
Dialogue: 100,0:01:38.44,0:01:42.02,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}睡眠是诅咒 一个必须承受的诅咒\N{\rENG}Sleep is a curse, and yet a curse I need to live. 
Dialogue: 100,0:01:42.02,0:01:43.19,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}--史蒂文·宇宙\N{\rENG}Steven Universe. 
Dialogue: 100,0:01:43.58,0:01:45.02,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}史蒂文不像我们\N{\rENG}Steven isn't like us. 
Dialogue: 100,0:01:45.03,0:01:46.34,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}他需要休息\N{\rENG}He needs rest. 
Dialogue: 100,0:01:46.54,0:01:48.18,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你们就不用休息吗?\N{\rENG}Don't you guys need rest, too? 
Dialogue: 100,0:01:48.56,0:01:49.86,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你们看起来很疲惫\N{\rENG}You look exhausted. 
Dialogue: 100,0:01:50.92,0:01:52.53,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我们好极了\N{\rENG}We look awesome. 
Dialogue: 100,0:01:52.94,0:01:55.10,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}听着 没试过\N{\rENG}Look, you can't really knock sleep
Dialogue: 100,0:01:55.10,0:01:56.17,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}就没有发言权\N{\rENG}until you try it. 
Dialogue: 100,0:01:56.17,0:01:59.00,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}而且 也许我们可以搞个有趣的\N{\rENG}And maybe we can throw a little fun into the mix
Dialogue: 100,0:01:59.01,0:02:01.34,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}睡衣派对!\N{\rENG}with a slumber party! 
Dialogue: 100,0:02:01.34,0:02:02.88,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}有-有趣?\N{\rENG}F-fun? 
Dialogue: 100,0:02:02.88,0:02:03.58,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}对啊\N{\rENG}Yeah. 
Dialogue: 100,0:02:03.58,0:02:05.91,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我们所有人一起 安详的眯一觉\N{\rENG}All of us together, peacefully dozing off. 
Dialogue: 100,0:02:06.22,0:02:07.50,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}就当外面没有\N{\rENG}It'll be like there isn't
Dialogue: 100,0:02:07.50,0:02:10.18,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}一个满是复仇念头的融合体在用仇恨煮沸大海\N{\rENG}a vengeful fusion boiling the ocean with hatred. 
Dialogue: 100,0:02:10.36,0:02:11.58,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}史蒂文是对的\N{\rENG}Steven's right. 
Dialogue: 100,0:02:11.59,0:02:14.09,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你们应该呆在家休息 但我得离开\N{\rENG}You should stay here and relax, but I'm going. 
Dialogue: 100,0:02:14.64,0:02:16.36,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}因为我永远都是放松的\N{\rENG}'Cause I'm always relaxed. 
Dialogue: 100,0:02:16.36,0:02:19.04,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}但石榴 你不可能\N{\rENG}But Garnet, you couldn't possibly
Dialogue: 100,0:02:19.04,0:02:20.36,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}一个人搜索整片海洋\N{\rENG}search the ocean by yourself. 
Dialogue: 100,0:02:20.36,0:02:24.03,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}让我-让我们帮你吧\N{\rENG}Let me--let us help you. 
Dialogue: 100,0:02:24.03,0:02:25.36,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我们是一个团队\N{\rENG}We're a team. 
Dialogue: 100,0:02:25.37,0:02:26.04,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}不用\N{\rENG}No. 
Dialogue: 100,0:02:26.08,0:02:29.44,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}现在你们是一个团队-睡衣团队\N{\rENG}Right now, you're a party--a slumber party. 
Dialogue: 100,0:02:29.68,0:02:31.70,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}史蒂文 带着些宝石人上床\N{\rENG}Steven, put these gems to bed. 
Dialogue: 100,0:02:31.82,0:02:33.04,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}不要熬夜哦\N{\rENG}Don't stay up too late. 
Dialogue: 100,0:02:33.18,0:02:34.77,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}冰箱里有零食\N{\rENG}There's snacks in the fridge. 
Dialogue: 100,0:02:34.78,0:02:36.58,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}再见\N{\rENG}Bye. 
Dialogue: 100,0:02:36.78,0:02:39.21,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}现在 在开始睡衣派对之前\N{\rENG}Now, before we get this slumber party started, 
Dialogue: 100,0:02:39.21,0:02:41.91,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你们有人想要睡衣伙伴吗?\N{\rENG}would either of you care for a slumber companion? 
Dialogue: 100,0:02:42.10,0:02:42.72,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我不用\N{\rENG}I'm good. 
Dialogue: 100,0:02:47.00,0:02:47.60,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}珍珠?\N{\rENG} Pearl? 
Dialogue: 100,0:02:47.62,0:02:49.39,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我不需要睡衣伙伴\N{\rENG}I'll pass on the slumber pals. 
Dialogue: 100,0:02:49.39,0:02:51.49,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}好吧. 入睡吧\N{\rENG}Okay. Sleep it up, then. 
Dialogue: 100,0:02:51.49,0:02:52.74,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}噢 好吧\N{\rENG}Oh, right. 
Dialogue: 100,0:02:54.10,0:02:55.44,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}这样对吗?\N{\rENG}Is this right? 
Dialogue: 100,0:02:55.56,0:02:57.64,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}不 你得躺下\N{\rENG}No, you should lay down. 
Dialogue: 100,0:02:57.92,0:02:59.02,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我知道了\N{\rENG}I get it now. 
Dialogue: 100,0:03:00.80,0:03:01.68,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}这样对吗?\N{\rENG}Am I doing it? 
Dialogue: 100,0:03:01.80,0:03:04.24,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}呃 这比刚才好多了\N{\rENG}Well, that's way better than before. 
Dialogue: 100,0:03:04.38,0:03:05.96,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}但 一定要保持闭眼\N{\rENG}But close your eyes all the way. 
Dialogue: 100,0:03:06.60,0:03:10.08,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}好. 好的. 我在睡觉\N{\rENG}Okay. All right. I'm sleeping now. 
Dialogue: 100,0:03:10.74,0:03:11.58,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我在睡觉\N{\rENG}I'm sleeping. 
Dialogue: 100,0:03:11.66,0:03:13.48,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你睡觉时不能说话\N{\rENG}You can't talk while you sleep. 
Dialogue: 100,0:03:13.82,0:03:15.75,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}到底怎么才能入睡?\N{\rENG}How's this even supposed to work? 
Dialogue: 100,0:03:15.75,0:03:16.94,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}这很简单\N{\rENG}It's easy. 
Dialogue: 100,0:03:17.15,0:03:21.48,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你只要躺下 怎么舒服怎么来 不要乱动\N{\rENG}You just lie down, get nice and comfy, don't move, 
Dialogue: 100,0:03:21.82,0:03:26.29,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}而且不要想任何事情\N{\rENG}and don't think about anything. 
Dialogue: 100,0:03:26.29,0:03:29.63,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}"宇宙小子"在演播室现场观众面前实时录制\N{\rENG}Steven Universe was filmed before a live studio audience. 
