Dialogue: 100,0:03:29.63,0:03:30.68,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}哦 我的天哪 \N{\rENG}Oh, my goodness, 
Dialogue: 100,0:03:30.70,0:03:32.93,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}康妮马上就到了\N{\rENG}Connie's going to be here any second now. 
Dialogue: 100,0:03:32.93,0:03:33.97,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我简直不敢相信\N{\rENG}I can't believe it. 
Dialogue: 100,0:03:33.98,0:03:35.68,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你的第一次校园舞会!\N{\rENG}Your first school dance. 
Dialogue: 100,0:03:35.68,0:03:37.36,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}让我调整一下你的领带并-\N{\rENG}Let me just fix your tie and--
Dialogue: 100,0:03:37.36,0:03:39.34,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}别再把史蒂文当个宝宝拉\N{\rENG}Stop fussing over Steven like a baby. 
Dialogue: 100,0:03:39.34,0:03:41.00,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}紫晶 我是怎么跟你说的\N{\rENG}Amethyst, what did I tell you
Dialogue: 100,0:03:41.00,0:03:42.68,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}别在屋里滑那个\N{\rENG}about riding that thing in the house? 
Dialogue: 100,0:03:42.74,0:03:44.34,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}祝你舞会玩的愉快 伙计\N{\rENG}Have fun at your dance, dude. 
Dialogue: 100,0:03:44.35,0:03:46.94,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}\N{\rENG}Oh! Bungacowa! 
Dialogue: 600,0:03:44.35,0:03:46.94,Hint,,0,0,0,,"Bungacowa!"是"Cowabunga!"的倒装词. 这是美漫中一个表达兴奋的惯用语.\N最初起源于漫画"史努比"并由"忍者神龟"和Bart Simpson( 巴特-辛普森一家) 发扬光大
Dialogue: 100,0:03:46.94,0:03:49.42,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}紫晶 别让我抓到你!\N{\rENG}Amethyst, I'm gonna get you! 
Dialogue: 100,0:03:49.60,0:03:50.98,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}马上 康妮\N{\rENG}Just a second, Connie. 
Dialogue: 100,0:03:51.10,0:03:54.04,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你绝对猜不到紫晶刚刚-蛤?\N{\rENG}You won't believe what Amethyst just--huh? 
Dialogue: 100,0:03:54.99,0:03:56.92,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我能为你做什么吗?\N{\rENG}Can I help you? 
Dialogue: 100,0:03:58.42,0:04:00.12,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}该放松了!\N{\rENG}Chille tid. 
Dialogue: 100,0:04:00.96,0:04:03.13,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}哦 你好 石榴--嘿 史蒂文\N{\rENG}Oh, hi, Garnet. Hey, Steven. 
Dialogue: 100,0:04:03.13,0:04:04.83,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你今晚一定要来沙滩上\N{\rENG}You got to come to the beach tonight. 
Dialogue: 100,0:04:04.83,0:04:07.30,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}到时会有个篝火派对哦!\N{\rENG}There's gonna be this huge bonfire party thing. 
Dialogue: 100,0:04:07.30,0:04:08.57,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我去不了\N{\rENG}I can't go to that. 
Dialogue: 100,0:04:08.84,0:04:11.48,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我要和康妮参加一个大型舞会呢\N{\rENG}I'm going to the big dance with Connie. 
Dialogue: 100,0:04:11.58,0:04:13.40,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}喔 盛大的舞会\N{\rENG}Wow. The big dance. 
Dialogue: 100,0:04:13.60,0:04:15.52,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}别做出格的事哦\N{\rENG}Don't do anything I wouldn't do. 
Dialogue: 100,0:04:18.28,0:04:19.08,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}她来了!\N{\rENG} She's here! 
Dialogue: 100,0:04:19.21,0:04:22.05,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}好啦 我准备好去跳舞了 康-\N{\rENG}Okay, I'm ready for the big dance con--
Dialogue: 100,0:04:22.24,0:04:22.58,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}呃?\N{\rENG}huh? 
Dialogue: 100,0:04:25.02,0:04:25.70,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}青金石?\N{\rENG}Lapis? 
Dialogue: 100,0:04:32.06,0:04:32.99,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你还好吗?\N{\rENG} Are you okay? 
Dialogue: 100,0:04:32.99,0:04:33.86,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}\N{\rENG}Ah! Ugh! 
Dialogue: 100,0:04:34.62,0:04:35.49,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}哦 妈呀...\N{\rENG}Oh, man...
Dialogue: 100,0:04:35.74,0:04:38.10,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我睡着了 然后做了个奇怪的梦\N{\rENG}I feel asleep and had this weird dream. 
Dialogue: 100,0:04:38.54,0:04:41.26,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我打开门 青金石在门外 然后-\N{\rENG}I opened the door and Lapis was there, and--
Dialogue: 100,0:04:41.26,0:04:42.74,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}呃 这听起来毫无逻辑\N{\rENG}well, that doesn't make any sense. 
Dialogue: 100,0:04:42.74,0:04:45.50,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}青金石正和碧玉在海底融合在一起\N{\rENG}Lapis is fused with Jasper at the bottom of the ocean. 
Dialogue: 100,0:04:46.28,0:04:48.60,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你从没做过梦吧?\N{\rENG}You've never had a dream before, huh? 
Dialogue: 100,0:04:48.60,0:04:50.66,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}哦...我觉得没有\N{\rENG}Uh...I don't think so. 
Dialogue: 100,0:04:50.90,0:04:53.96,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}好吧 珍珠 梦并不总是合理的\N{\rENG}Well, Pearl, dreams don't always make sense. 
Dialogue: 100,0:04:54.40,0:04:56.24,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}当你作梦时 你脑中的想法\N{\rENG}When you dream, the thoughts in your head
Dialogue: 100,0:04:56.24,0:04:58.08,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}混合在一起 组成一部诡异的影片\N{\rENG}get all mixed up into a weird movie. 
Dialogue: 100,0:04:58.56,0:04:59.96,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}并且它们很难解释 \N{\rENG}And they're really hard to explain, 
Dialogue: 100,0:04:59.96,0:05:01.70,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}让其看起来很无聊\N{\rENG}which is why they're boring to listen to. 
Dialogue: 100,0:05:02.48,0:05:04.04,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}就像 有一次 \N{\rENG}Like. this one time, 
Dialogue: 100,0:05:04.04,0:05:06.88,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我做了个梦 好像 有些东西\N{\rENG}I had a dream where, like, these things
Dialogue: 100,0:05:06.88,0:05:08.90,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}挂在甜甜圈店里出售 对吧?\N{\rENG}were being sold at the big donut, right? 
Dialogue: 100,0:05:08.90,0:05:11.14,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}但是甜甜圈店的前门\N{\rENG}But the front door of the big donut shop
Dialogue: 100,0:05:11.14,0:05:13.36,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}却连接到了我爸面包车的后面\N{\rENG}led to the back of my dad's van. 
Dialogue: 100,0:05:13.50,0:05:15.50,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}于是 我走进了面包车 \N{\rENG}So, I go into the van, 
Dialogue: 100,0:05:15.64,0:05:19.00,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}然后狮子因为某些原因在开车 但...\N{\rENG}and Lion is driving for some reason, but...
Dialogue: 100,0:05:19.00,0:05:21.28,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}...他开得非常好\N{\rENG}...he's driving really well. 
Dialogue: 100,0:05:22.28,0:05:25.94,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}然后-然后我对他说 我说 "狮子-"\N{\rENG}And--and then I say to him, I says, "Lion--"
Dialogue: 100,0:05:27.25,0:05:31.38,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}"狮子 你是怎么学会开面-面包车的?"\N{\rENG}"Lion, how did you learn to drive you a v-van? 
Dialogue: 100,0:05:31.39,0:05:32.78,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}"你甚至不能"\N{\rENG}You can't even...
Dialogue: 100,0:05:32.79,0:05:37.96,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}"你...你都不能给我...我的..."\N{\rENG}You...You can't bring...Me...My...
Dialogue: 100,0:05:39.74,0:05:41.00,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}\N{\rENG}Whoo! 
Dialogue: 600,0:05:39.74,0:05:42.74,Hint,,0,0,0,,此处史蒂文用背上的螺旋桨飞行的画面致敬"屋顶上的小飞人"中的"Karlsson"( 卡尔松)\N"屋顶上的小飞人"是一部由瑞典作家Astrid Lindgren创作的儿童系列读物
Dialogue: 100,0:05:43.50,0:05:44.70,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}狗升机!\N{\rENG} Dogcopter! 
Dialogue: 100,0:05:44.70,0:05:47.68,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}先生 我是您最忠实的粉丝之一!\N{\rENG}Mr. copter, sir, I'm one of your biggest fans! 
Dialogue: 100,0:05:47.68,0:05:49.60,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}求求你能给我个签名吗?\N{\rENG}Can I please have your autograph? 
Dialogue: 100,0:05:51.17,0:05:53.82,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}狗升机先生 求求您-嘿 等等我!\N{\rENG}Mr. copter, please--hey, wait! 
Dialogue: 100,0:05:53.82,0:05:54.98,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}您要去哪?\N{\rENG}Where are you going? 
Dialogue: 100,0:05:55.82,0:05:58.30,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我希望小报中有关狗升机先生的流言\N{\rENG}I hope the rumors about dogcopter in the tabloids
Dialogue: 100,0:05:58.30,0:05:59.24,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}都不是真的\N{\rENG}aren't true. 
Dialogue: 100,0:05:59.82,0:06:01.94,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}嗯? 哦 嘿 珍珠!\N{\rENG}Huh? Oh, hey, Pearl! 
Dialogue: 100,0:06:02.40,0:06:04.32,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}等等...别吃我啊!\N{\rENG}Wait...Don't eat me! 
Dialogue: 100,0:06:05.48,0:06:07.32,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}噗! 唔! 哦 天哪\N{\rENG}Ptoo! Ooh! Oh, man. 
Dialogue: 100,0:06:07.50,0:06:09.34,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}谢谢你给的升级组件 珍珠!\N{\rENG}Thanks for the upgrade, Pearl! 
Dialogue: 600,0:06:07.50,0:06:09.34,Hint,,0,0,0,,这个很明显了 "铁臂阿童木"
Dialogue: 100,0:06:09.54,0:06:11.38,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}现在我能追上狗-\N{\rENG}Now I can catch up with dog--
Dialogue: 100,0:06:11.79,0:06:13.30,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}喔 紫晶?\N{\rENG}whoa. Amethyst? 
Dialogue: 100,0:06:14.93,0:06:16.09,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}\N{\rENG}Hmm. 
Dialogue: 100,0:06:16.10,0:06:18.26,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}这一切 真的开始变得诡异了\N{\rENG}This is getting really weird. 
Dialogue: 100,0:06:18.46,0:06:19.67,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}这确实很诡异\N{\rENG}This is weird. 
Dialogue: 100,0:06:19.88,0:06:22.03,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}嘿 那声音听起来很像-\N{\rENG}Hey, that sounds a lot like--
Dialogue: 100,0:06:22.04,0:06:23.14,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}史蒂文!\N{\rENG}Steven! 
Dialogue: 100,0:06:23.14,0:06:24.60,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}青金石!\N{\rENG}Lapis Lazuli! 
Dialogue: 100,0:06:24.86,0:06:27.44,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}史蒂文 你-你在这干什么?\N{\rENG}Steven, wh-what are you doing in here? 
Dialogue: 100,0:06:27.44,0:06:30.78,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}呃 我知道这听起来很怪 但我正在做梦 \N{\rENG}Uh, I know it's weird, but I'm just dreaming, 
Dialogue: 100,0:06:30.78,0:06:32.11,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}所以不用担心\N{\rENG}so don't even worry about it. 
Dialogue: 100,0:06:32.11,0:06:33.35,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}什么? 不!\N{\rENG}What? No! 
Dialogue: 100,0:06:33.60,0:06:36.18,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}史蒂文 我正试着集中注意力\N{\rENG}Steven, I'm trying to concentrate. 
Dialogue: 100,0:06:36.18,0:06:37.62,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你怎么会在这里?\N{\rENG} How are you here? 
Dialogue: 100,0:06:37.78,0:06:39.32,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}哦 我的天哪 你还好吗?\N{\rENG}Oh, my gosh. Are you okay? 
Dialogue: 100,0:06:39.46,0:06:41.26,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}史蒂文 求求你 我-\N{\rENG}Steven, please, I--
Dialogue: 100,0:06:45.70,0:06:46.68,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}呃...青金石!\N{\rENG}Ugh...Lapis! 
Dialogue: 100,0:06:47.80,0:06:48.52,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}紫晶?\N{\rENG}Amethyst? 
Dialogue: 100,0:06:49.16,0:06:51.10,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}嘿 你在笑什么?\N{\rENG}Hey, what are you laughing at? 
Dialogue: 100,0:06:53.88,0:06:57.00,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}噢 罗丝! 这真是太好了!\N{\rENG}Oh, Rose! This is wonderful! 
Dialogue: 100,0:06:57.00,0:07:01.12,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}跟你在一起非常开心 罗丝!\N{\rENG}I'm just having so much fun spending time with you, Rose! 
Dialogue: 600,0:06:57.00,0:06:59.00,Hint,,0,0,0,,这个太明显了 "泰坦尼克号"中Jack和Rose( 啧啧) 在船首的镜头
Dialogue: 100,0:07:01.52,0:07:04.64,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}忘了格雷格吧 我们一起在银河系旅游!\N{\rENG}Forget about Greg. Let's go travel the galaxy! 
Dialogue: 100,0:07:04.65,0:07:07.88,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}珍珠 非常感谢你...\N{\rENG}Pearl, thank you so much...
Dialogue: 100,0:07:07.88,0:07:10.05,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}修好我的车!\N{\rENG}For fixing my van! 
Dialogue: 600,0:07:07.88,0:07:10.05,Hint,,0,0,0,,详见第一季第27集
Dialogue: 100,0:07:10.05,0:07:11.58,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}哦! 啊!\N{\rENG}Oh! Ugh! 
Dialogue: 100,0:07:11.59,0:07:13.22,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}呕...\N{\rENG}Blegh...
Dialogue: 100,0:07:13.22,0:07:14.32,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}恶...\N{\rENG}Gah! 
Dialogue: 100,0:07:17.98,0:07:18.60,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}珍珠?\N{\rENG}Pearl? 
Dialogue: 100,0:07:19.03,0:07:21.36,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}呃...好的 史蒂文?\N{\rENG}Uh...Yes, Steven? 
Dialogue: 100,0:07:21.62,0:07:24.28,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我又做了 一个有关青金石的梦\N{\rENG}I had another dream about Lapis. 
Dialogue: 100,0:07:24.44,0:07:27.28,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}噢...没什么! 梦不是真实的!\N{\rENG}Oh...That's okay! Dreams aren't real! 
Dialogue: 100,0:07:27.30,0:07:29.36,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}那只是拼接电影!\N{\rENG}They're just mixed-up movies! 
Dialogue: 100,0:07:29.36,0:07:32.24,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}但我-我觉得我当时在和她对话\N{\rENG}But I--I think I was talking to her. 
Dialogue: 100,0:07:32.24,0:07:34.51,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}等等 你怎么知道的?\N{\rENG}Wait. How do you know? 
Dialogue: 100,0:07:34.51,0:07:37.04,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我不知道 但我能感觉到\N{\rENG}I don't, but I could just feel it. 
Dialogue: 100,0:07:37.04,0:07:38.14,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}她在喊叫\N{\rENG}She was yelling, 
Dialogue: 100,0:07:38.14,0:07:40.01,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}并且她真的受到刺激了\N{\rENG}and she was really freaked out. 
Dialogue: 100,0:07:40.01,0:07:43.01,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}她说了什么? 她还能控制住吗?\N{\rENG}What did she say? Is she still in control? 
Dialogue: 100,0:07:43.02,0:07:45.38,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我...我不知道\N{\rENG}I...I don't know. 
Dialogue: 100,0:07:45.39,0:07:48.22,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}史蒂文 你刚才可能通过你的梦境\N{\rENG}Steven, you could be using your dreams
Dialogue: 100,0:07:48.22,0:07:50.46,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}与她进行了心灵感应\N{\rENG}to connect with her mentally. 
Dialogue: 100,0:07:50.46,0:07:51.72,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你能再做一次吗?\N{\rENG}Can you do it again? 
Dialogue: 100,0:07:51.73,0:07:54.53,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}也许青金石刚好能告诉你她们在哪\N{\rENG}Maybe Lapis can just tell you where they are. 
Dialogue: 100,0:07:54.90,0:07:56.60,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我猜我又得入睡了\N{\rENG}I guess I have to go back to sleep. 
Dialogue: 100,0:07:57.04,0:07:59.03,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}快 珍珠 告诉我你的梦\N{\rENG}Quick, Pearl, tell me about your dream
Dialogue: 100,0:07:59.03,0:08:00.20,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}帮我入睡\N{\rENG}so I can fall asleep. 
Dialogue: 100,0:08:00.20,0:08:01.26,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我-我的梦?\N{\rENG}M-my dream? 
Dialogue: 100,0:08:01.26,0:08:04.24,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}来啊 珍珠! 这是为了大局!\N{\rENG}Come on, Pearl! It's for the greater good! 
Dialogue: 100,0:08:05.76,0:08:06.74,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}如果我必须的话\N{\rENG}If I must. 
Dialogue: 100,0:08:07.92,0:08:10.10,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}好吧 在我的梦里 我正-\N{\rENG} So, in my dream, I was--
Dialogue: 100,0:08:10.28,0:08:10.72,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}哦?\N{\rENG} What? 
Dialogue: 100,0:08:12.22,0:08:12.92,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}\N{\rENG} Wow! 
Dialogue: 100,0:08:13.16,0:08:14.26,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}他这就睡着了\N{\rENG}He been sleep. 
Dialogue: 100,0:08:17.00,0:08:19.28,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}噢! 我知道这已经是梦了\N{\rENG}Oh! I know this is a dream now, 
Dialogue: 100,0:08:19.72,0:08:22.06,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}那么我能想象出任何我想要的\N{\rENG}so I can imagine anything I want. 
Dialogue: 100,0:08:22.56,0:08:25.16,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}呃...土豆泥\N{\rENG}Uh...Mashed potato. 
Dialogue: 100,0:08:25.16,0:08:26.29,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}\N{\rENG}Hmm. 
Dialogue: 100,0:08:26.40,0:08:28.16,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}现在 我该怎么找到青金石?\N{\rENG}Now how do I find Lapis? 
Dialogue: 100,0:08:28.40,0:08:29.83,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}不是青金石\N{\rENG}Not Lapis. 
Dialogue: 100,0:08:29.83,0:08:31.26,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}不是青金石～\N{\rENG}Not Lapis. 
Dialogue: 100,0:08:31.27,0:08:32.76,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}不是青金石-\N{\rENG}Not Lapis. 
Dialogue: 100,0:08:32.77,0:08:34.60,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}呃! 狮子?\N{\rENG}Ugh! Lion? 
Dialogue: 100,0:08:34.88,0:08:37.14,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}等等 你不是狮子\N{\rENG}Wait. You're not Lion. 
Dialogue: 100,0:08:37.14,0:08:38.06,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}\N{\rENG}Whoa! 
Dialogue: 100,0:08:38.26,0:08:39.57,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}\N{\rENG}Aah! Ugh! 
Dialogue: 100,0:08:39.57,0:08:42.11,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}嗷 这是什么地方?\N{\rENG}Ow. What is this place? 
Dialogue: 100,0:08:43.70,0:08:44.44,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}青金石!\N{\rENG} Lapis! 
Dialogue: 100,0:08:44.90,0:08:45.56,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}史蒂文!\N{\rENG}Steven! 
Dialogue: 100,0:08:45.78,0:08:47.96,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你为什么总是-跑回来?!\N{\rENG}Why do you keep coming back? 
Dialogue: 600,0:08:45.78,0:08:47.96,Hint,,0,0,0,,此处青金石与碧玉被链条连接在一起的设定致敬"Jojo奇幻大冒险"中的Chain Necklace Deathmatch( 颈链死斗) 
Dialogue: 100,0:08:48.12,0:08:49.31,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我不能被分心!\N{\rENG}I can't get distracted! 
Dialogue: 100,0:08:49.32,0:08:51.04,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我-我得把我们困在海底\N{\rENG}I-I've got to hold us down
Dialogue: 100,0:08:51.04,0:08:53.30,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}借助你的星球的-海洋-的重量\N{\rENG}with the weight of your planet's ocean. 
Dialogue: 100,0:08:53.30,0:08:55.42,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我-必须-将她...\N{\rENG} I've got to keep her...
Dialogue: 100,0:08:56.78,0:08:58.64,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}等等 青金石 告诉我你们在哪\N{\rENG}Wait, Lapis, tell me where you are. 
Dialogue: 100,0:08:58.66,0:08:59.82,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我们能帮你\N{\rENG}We can help you. 
Dialogue: 100,0:09:01.54,0:09:03.54,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我告诉过你! 不!\N{\rENG}I told you! No! 
Dialogue: 100,0:09:04.12,0:09:04.68,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}\N{\rENG}Aah! 
Dialogue: 100,0:09:11.98,0:09:13.54,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}是你!!!\N{\rENG}You! 
Dialogue: 100,0:09:13.64,0:09:14.70,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}碧玉!\N{\rENG}Jasper! 
Dialogue: 100,0:09:15.54,0:09:16.68,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}是你!!!\N{\rENG}You! 
Dialogue: 100,0:09:17.11,0:09:18.78,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你-你!\N{\rENG}You! You! 
Dialogue: 100,0:09:18.98,0:09:20.24,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}\N{\rENG}Gaah! 
Dialogue: 100,0:09:21.24,0:09:23.66,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}噢! 不!!!!!\N{\rENG}Ohh! No! 
Dialogue: 100,0:09:26.34,0:09:27.24,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}青金石!\N{\rENG}Lapis! 
Dialogue: 100,0:09:27.58,0:09:28.52,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你看不出来吗?\N{\rENG}Can't you see? 
Dialogue: 100,0:09:28.82,0:09:31.29,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我不能停下来 哪怕一秒也不行\N{\rENG}I can't stop, not for a second. 
Dialogue: 100,0:09:31.56,0:09:32.86,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}不要再找我了\N{\rENG}Don't look for me. 
Dialogue: 100,0:09:33.14,0:09:35.50,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我不想要你的帮助. 但-\N{\rENG}I don't want your help. B-but--
Dialogue: 100,0:09:35.66,0:09:37.42,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}就让我为你做这些吧!\N{\rENG}just let me do this for you! 
Dialogue: 100,0:09:37.42,0:09:39.30,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}青金石...不!\N{\rENG}Lapis...No! 
Dialogue: 100,0:09:39.30,0:09:41.63,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我不再是...青金石了\N{\rENG}I'm not Lapis anymore. 
Dialogue: 600,0:09:41.63,0:09:43.54,Hint,,0,0,0,,有没有感觉此处像是"火影忍者"中的绝吗? 
Dialogue: 100,0:09:43.54,0:09:45.60,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我们现在是 孔雀石\N{\rENG}We're Malachite now. 
Dialogue: 100,0:09:45.97,0:09:47.34,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}青金石 不!\N{\rENG}Lapis, no! 
Dialogue: 100,0:09:52.98,0:09:55.98,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}\N{\rENG}Oooragh! 
Dialogue: 100,0:10:00.34,0:10:01.14,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}快走!\N{\rENG}Go! 
Dialogue: 100,0:10:01.14,0:10:02.00,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}青金石!\N{\rENG}Lapis! 
Dialogue: 100,0:10:03.04,0:10:05.06,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}史蒂文 没事了 我们就在这\N{\rENG}Steven, it's okay. We're here. 
Dialogue: 100,0:10:05.32,0:10:06.26,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你看到她了吗?\N{\rENG}Did you see her? 
Dialogue: 100,0:10:06.54,0:10:08.54,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}是的 她还在融合体中\N{\rENG}Yeah. She's still fused. 
Dialogue: 100,0:10:08.80,0:10:11.64,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}而且她还能控制住 但我不知道还能坚持多久\N{\rENG}And she's still in control, but I don't know for how long. 
Dialogue: 100,0:10:11.64,0:10:12.20,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}并且-\N{\rENG}And--
Dialogue: 100,0:10:14.88,0:10:16.80,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}这 真是个奇怪的派对\N{\rENG}This is a weird party. 
Dialogue: 100,0:10:17.00,0:10:18.27,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}石榴!\N{\rENG}Garnet! Mm. 
Dialogue: 100,0:10:18.42,0:10:20.22,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}史蒂文 你还没睡着\N{\rENG}Steven, you're still awake. 
Dialogue: 100,0:10:21.04,0:10:22.50,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}紫晶刚才在滑滑板\N{\rENG}Amethyst was on a skateboard. 
Dialogue: 100,0:10:22.64,0:10:24.16,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}接着狗升机对着我"喵"了一下\N{\rENG}And then dogcopter meowed at me
Dialogue: 100,0:10:24.16,0:10:26.52,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}而且对我说的没有任何兴趣!\N{\rENG}and was just not interested in what I had to say at all! 
Dialogue: 100,0:10:26.72,0:10:28.46,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}也许我有些问题需要解决...\N{\rENG}And I might have some issues I need to work out...
Dialogue: 100,0:10:28.46,0:10:30.96,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}但青金石 她就在外面 而且她仍然-\N{\rENG}But Lapis, she's out there, and she's still--
Dialogue: 100,0:10:30.96,0:10:32.45,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}嘘～嘘～嘘～嘘--\N{\rENG}shh, shh, shh, shh. 
Dialogue: 100,0:10:32.66,0:10:33.72,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我知道你很担心 \N{\rENG}I know you're worried, 
Dialogue: 100,0:10:33.72,0:10:35.62,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}但现在我们什么也做不了\N{\rENG}but there's nothing we can do right now. 
Dialogue: 100,0:10:35.62,0:10:38.09,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}所以让我们放松一下\N{\rENG}So let's take it easy. 
Dialogue: 100,0:10:38.09,0:10:40.13,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我来告诉你们该怎么做\N{\rENG}I'll show you how it's done. 
Dialogue: 100,0:10:42.53,0:10:44.20,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}这还真有说服力啊\N{\rENG}That's pretty convincing. 
Dialogue: 100,0:10:44.20,0:10:45.86,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}石榴?\N{\rENG}Garnet? 
